    "paragraph-d178ea3cc1ae": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "可变形部件模型 (DPM) ("
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "http://people.cs.uchicago.edu/~pff/papers/lsvm-pami.pdf"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Felzenszwalb 等人，2010"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ") 通过可变形部件的混合图模型（马尔可夫随机场）识别对象。该模型由三个主要组件组成："
        }
      ]
    },
    "list-item-953991aeb643": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "一个粗略的"
        },
